doc.title: Law & Order: Special Victims Unit

credit.role: Crime Scene Unit Investigator, Customs/Airport Traveler, Pedestrian
Mitch Wilkens, aka Max Van Horn

doc.plot: This show delves into the dark side of the New York underworld as the detectives of a new elite force, the Special Victims Unit, investigate and prosecute various sexually oriented crimes, while trying to balance the effects of the investigation on their own lives.
